            <Title>Locations</Title>
            <Text>The Wastes - imagine… sand worms, but small, they burrow into your skin :) 
Tin Town - shanty town energy, very close to Bank
Fauve Plaza - HAHAHA… the center of the richest district in all of Technocraft, the space where elites give speeches.
The Corporeal Spa - the secret spa in the Aliment district where people can get normal spa services or can also get new body parts or parts cut off/adjusted. 
Triflat - the suburb on the sea that bianca comes from. There are a lot of major pharmaceutical companies here, Bianca’s parents work at them, the normal thing is to go to a good school to work at them. There are pretty parks here and lots of places to connect to nature.
Bank - the bottom tip of the island that Technocraft sits on… Klygore grew up here
